high_descs: Turn around, walk towards the fridge, turn left towards the stove, and turn right to where the dishwasher is at.
Open the cabinet to the left of the dishwasher and take out the green sponge from it.
Turn around, take a step forward, and then turn left towards the fridge.
Place the sponge in the bowl in the fridge.
Take the bowl with the sponge out of the fridge.
Turn to your left and find the cabinet at the right corner from you.
Open the cabinet and place the bowl along with the sponge in the cabinet.
